1
00:00:07,220 --> 00:00:11,820
♪She looks at the bright moon
hanging high above the clouds♪

2
00:00:11,860 --> 00:00:14,140
♪And I fall into the mountains♪

3
00:00:14,220 --> 00:00:16,100
♪Protect this broken world♪

4
00:00:16,180 --> 00:00:20,620
♪A faint wish♪

5
00:00:20,660 --> 00:00:23,900
♪Life is just a dream,
isn't the world so?♪

6
00:00:23,980 --> 00:00:27,620
♪Looking back,
I count the joys of my remaining years♪

7
00:00:27,700 --> 00:00:31,020
♪It's difficult to see you in my dreams♪

8
00:00:31,060 --> 00:00:33,940
♪Ignoring the coldness of the world,
I still linger♪

9
00:00:33,980 --> 00:00:37,300
♪Love and hate are intertwined,
not just in the past♪

10
00:00:37,340 --> 00:00:40,900
♪The past is painful,
and time goes by in a flash♪

11
00:00:40,940 --> 00:00:44,500
♪Stars fall on the mountain top again♪

12
00:00:44,580 --> 00:00:48,140
♪My heart is as pure as the moon
and connected to you♪

13
00:00:54,140 --> 00:00:56,980
[No One But You]

14
00:00:56,980 --> 00:01:01,980
[Episode 2]
[It is my scar and the sun you gave me.]

15
00:01:15,780 --> 00:01:16,820
Don't forget.

16
00:01:17,660 --> 00:01:20,260
You and I killed the culprit together.

17
00:01:33,900 --> 00:01:34,940
You must remember.

18
00:01:37,020 --> 00:01:38,860
Desire is like a chain.

19
00:01:40,980 --> 00:01:43,060
It can make people willingly

20
00:01:44,380 --> 00:01:45,860
become prisoners

21
00:01:47,060 --> 00:01:48,740
and be manipulated.

22
00:01:50,500 --> 00:01:51,300
At the end,

23
00:01:53,260 --> 00:01:54,860
it take their lives.

24
00:02:10,820 --> 00:02:12,540
That was the correct demonstration.

25
00:02:15,580 --> 00:02:17,180
Your attempt just now was a fail.

26
00:02:17,980 --> 00:02:19,980
Your movements and techniques
were too clumsy.

27
00:02:22,260 --> 00:02:23,740
This is a fatal weakness.

28
00:02:25,220 --> 00:02:27,380
You are no longer
the person you were five years ago.

29
00:02:41,980 --> 00:02:43,140
What's the hurry?

30
00:02:52,900 --> 00:02:54,140
Qingqiu...

31
00:02:55,740 --> 00:02:56,860
Qingqiu!

32
00:02:59,620 --> 00:03:01,620
Don't come any closer!

33
00:03:13,140 --> 00:03:13,620
After her!

34
00:03:15,180 --> 00:03:16,060
Don't let her get away!

35
00:03:16,180 --> 00:03:16,620
Yes, Sir!

36
00:03:17,980 --> 00:03:18,660
This way!

37
00:03:19,460 --> 00:03:19,900
Hurry!

38
00:04:20,140 --> 00:04:21,420
If your heart is empty,

39
00:04:21,900 --> 00:04:23,780
fill it up with hatred.

40
00:04:34,900 --> 00:04:35,500
Not bad.

41
00:04:37,500 --> 00:04:38,700
You're improving quickly.

42
00:04:39,420 --> 00:04:40,620
You'll be able to

43
00:04:41,220 --> 00:04:42,180
undertake the mission alone.

44
00:04:43,340 --> 00:04:44,820
Your first mission

45
00:04:44,820 --> 00:04:46,940
is to eliminate the culprit
who killed your sister.

46
00:04:48,300 --> 00:04:49,460
If the mission fails,

47
00:04:50,020 --> 00:04:51,420
you will be discarded.

48
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:13,400
[Yu Qingqiu Jiang and Mohan are engaged]

49
00:05:19,860 --> 00:05:21,020
Finally, you saw it.

50
00:05:29,700 --> 00:05:31,420
You were my sister's fiancé?

51
00:05:41,980 --> 00:05:42,500
Yes.

52
00:05:45,780 --> 00:05:47,220
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

53
00:05:48,860 --> 00:05:50,260
Finding out now
makes no difference, right?

54
00:05:51,740 --> 00:05:53,660
If you had told me earlier, I...

55
00:05:57,740 --> 00:05:58,940
I wouldn't have...

56
00:06:06,940 --> 00:06:09,500
If he really had something
to do with Qingqiu's death,

57
00:06:09,980 --> 00:06:11,660
what should I do with myself?

58
00:06:13,060 --> 00:06:14,980
Your elder sister's death
has something to do with Jiang Mohan.

59
00:06:14,980 --> 00:06:17,140
If you want to know, meet me
at Military Governor's Mansion tomorrow.

60
00:06:20,060 --> 00:06:20,900
Regardless,

61
00:06:21,380 --> 00:06:22,540
I'll see what he has to say.

62
00:06:23,060 --> 00:06:24,660
I have to find a way
to lure the tiger away from the mountain.

63
00:06:27,540 --> 00:06:28,180
Sir.

64
00:06:28,540 --> 00:06:30,460
Yesterday's mission
was successfully completed.

65
00:06:31,100 --> 00:06:33,580
By the way, Beizhou seems to...

66
00:06:38,740 --> 00:06:39,380
Where is Qinghuan?

67
00:06:39,700 --> 00:06:40,660
Miss Yu just went out.

68
00:06:45,350 --> 00:06:50,940
[Beizhou Military Governor's Mansion]

69
00:06:50,940 --> 00:06:51,620
Are you okay?

70
00:06:51,860 --> 00:06:52,380
I'm fine.

71
00:06:52,860 --> 00:06:54,260
It seems to be
the assassin from yesterday.

72
00:06:54,660 --> 00:06:55,540
He went that way.

73
00:07:01,820 --> 00:07:03,420
Is this how you protect Miss Yu?

74
00:07:05,250 --> 00:07:08,920
[Beizhou Military Governor's Mansion]

75
00:07:14,980 --> 00:07:16,460
A bunch of good-for-nothings.

76
00:07:25,660 --> 00:07:27,820
Sir, the assassin
couldn't have gotten far,

77
00:07:27,820 --> 00:07:28,620
should we go after him?

78
00:07:33,260 --> 00:07:34,500
Stay in the mansion,

79
00:07:35,020 --> 00:07:35,700
don't go anywhere.

80
00:07:36,700 --> 00:07:37,100
Okay.

81
00:07:37,540 --> 00:07:38,220
You,

82
00:07:38,460 --> 00:07:39,140
follow me.

83
00:07:57,860 --> 00:07:58,700
Miss.

84
00:08:04,270 --> 00:08:07,120
[Young Leader of Qing Gang, Chu Yunfan]

85
00:08:16,500 --> 00:08:17,340
Miss Yu.

86
00:08:19,060 --> 00:08:20,220
I'm here, as promised.

87
00:08:23,300 --> 00:08:25,180
Yesterday, you attempted
to assassinate my brother-in-law,

88
00:08:25,460 --> 00:08:27,940
yet you dare to come alone today.

89
00:08:28,420 --> 00:08:30,180
You've got some nerve.

90
00:08:31,700 --> 00:08:33,460
You hold me in such high regard.

91
00:08:33,660 --> 00:08:35,700
It's worth my risking my life
coming here.

92
00:08:37,980 --> 00:08:39,580
Then you should know

93
00:08:39,820 --> 00:08:42,540
that my brother-in-law's enemy
is my enemy.

94
00:08:43,260 --> 00:08:44,940
If you really want to kill me,

95
00:08:45,500 --> 00:08:47,460
you wouldn't have bothered
to lure Jiang Mohan away

96
00:08:48,220 --> 00:08:49,580
or waited so long for me.

97
00:08:50,340 --> 00:08:51,140
Right?

98
00:08:52,620 --> 00:08:53,700
You've been watching me?

99
00:08:53,820 --> 00:08:56,180
Only you are worth my effort, Miss Yu.

100
00:08:56,500 --> 00:08:58,740
Jiang Mohan is not.

101
00:09:43,820 --> 00:09:44,660
You are...

102
00:09:45,780 --> 00:09:46,620
Fan?

103
00:09:50,340 --> 00:09:52,300
You look different from before.

104
00:09:54,500 --> 00:09:56,100
I didn't expect that years have past

105
00:09:56,460 --> 00:09:58,300
and you have become
the young leader of the Qing Gang.

106
00:10:00,260 --> 00:10:01,380
I didn't expect

107
00:10:01,860 --> 00:10:03,580
you to become the boss of Joys of Life

108
00:10:03,700 --> 00:10:05,780
who manages the largest
intelligence network in Beizhou either.

109
00:10:07,860 --> 00:10:08,820
What I expected even less is

110
00:10:09,980 --> 00:10:12,740
that you would work for Jiang Mohan,
the murderous demon.

111
00:10:13,620 --> 00:10:15,220
No one knows him better than I do.

112
00:10:16,220 --> 00:10:18,700
If he didn't me years ago,

113
00:10:19,180 --> 00:10:21,140
I would have died long ago.

114
00:10:23,020 --> 00:10:23,820
So,

115
00:10:24,500 --> 00:10:26,780
what did you come here to tell me?

116
00:10:31,140 --> 00:10:33,100
The reason you went to so much trouble

117
00:10:34,340 --> 00:10:35,380
to lure me away is him?

118
00:10:45,250 --> 00:10:47,920
[Young Leader of Qing Gang, Chu Yunfan]

119
00:10:49,620 --> 00:10:51,180
As expected,
he is the young leader of the Qing Gang.

120
00:10:54,100 --> 00:10:55,300
Sure, only you

121
00:10:55,820 --> 00:10:58,100
are able to make such a big scene
in Beizhou.

122
00:11:05,220 --> 00:11:05,900
You...

123
00:11:07,500 --> 00:11:09,780
should know
the consequences of betraying me.

124
00:11:11,900 --> 00:11:14,700
Mohan, I would never betray you.

125
00:11:17,260 --> 00:11:18,740
I have to be fair.

126
00:11:19,460 --> 00:11:20,180
Sir.

127
00:11:20,660 --> 00:11:22,340
Just now, Miss Yu wanted to kill me

128
00:11:22,340 --> 00:11:23,420
for you.

129
00:11:24,380 --> 00:11:25,580
The more you protect her,

130
00:11:26,740 --> 00:11:29,180
the more I can't wait to kill you.

131
00:11:33,980 --> 00:11:37,500
What kind of death do you intend for me?

132
00:11:41,140 --> 00:11:43,020
Everyone in Beizhou knows

133
00:11:44,300 --> 00:11:47,260
that there are countless heads buried
in front of my mansion.

134
00:11:48,340 --> 00:11:50,620
But for you, Chu Yunfan,
I can make an exception.

135
00:11:55,020 --> 00:11:55,820
Shen Jun.

136
00:12:06,100 --> 00:12:06,780
Bury him alive.

137
00:12:07,340 --> 00:12:07,900
Yes, Sir.

138
00:12:07,900 --> 00:12:08,900
Sir.

139
00:12:16,260 --> 00:12:19,060
Then I'll have to be rude

140
00:12:19,060 --> 00:12:19,900
and borrow Miss Yu.

141
00:12:30,900 --> 00:12:32,860
I have never been threatened.

142
00:12:33,900 --> 00:12:35,900
The worst is
losing one more person's life.

143
00:12:37,140 --> 00:12:38,060
Did you hear that?

144
00:12:38,420 --> 00:12:40,860
It seems that you are insignificant
to him.

145
00:12:42,860 --> 00:12:43,860
No need to sow discord.

146
00:12:44,500 --> 00:12:46,740
Mohan saved my life.

147
00:12:47,420 --> 00:12:48,740
If he wants to take it back,

148
00:12:49,180 --> 00:12:50,580
I am willing to do so.

149
00:12:51,500 --> 00:12:52,940
Sir, you're willing to give up

150
00:12:52,940 --> 00:12:54,180
such a beautiful, understanding woman?

151
00:12:59,980 --> 00:13:01,420
How could I come unprepared

152
00:13:01,420 --> 00:13:02,740
to a fight with you?

153
00:13:04,740 --> 00:13:07,980
You dare to break into this mansion
with so few of you?

154
00:13:08,140 --> 00:13:09,780
You sure can dream.

155
00:13:10,020 --> 00:13:11,900
But it's not difficult
for us to perish together.

156
00:13:12,260 --> 00:13:14,020
However, I'm here today to negotiate.

157
00:13:14,140 --> 00:13:16,180
It depends on whether you're willing
to do me the honor.

158
00:13:27,420 --> 00:13:28,020
Stand down.

159
00:13:28,180 --> 00:13:28,980
- Yes, Sir.
- Yes, Sir.

160
00:13:39,220 --> 00:13:40,020
Let's talk.

161
00:13:41,540 --> 00:13:43,860
A month ago,
in order to seize the docks,

162
00:13:43,860 --> 00:13:45,500
you sent someone
to assassinate my father.

163
00:13:46,580 --> 00:13:49,060
Even now, he is still in a coma.

164
00:13:50,220 --> 00:13:51,620
I know it's very hard to kill you,

165
00:13:52,140 --> 00:13:53,260
so last night

166
00:13:54,060 --> 00:13:56,100
was just a small greeting gift.

167
00:13:56,460 --> 00:13:57,300
Tell me,

168
00:13:58,260 --> 00:13:59,340
what do you want?

169
00:14:01,660 --> 00:14:02,540
I want her.

170
00:14:18,460 --> 00:14:22,180
♪The waves♪

171
00:14:22,260 --> 00:14:26,460
♪When will you
stop looking through them?♪

172
00:14:26,540 --> 00:14:30,500
♪Missed the time
when the sun was restored♪

173
00:14:30,580 --> 00:14:34,660
♪What else do you expect to like?♪

174
00:14:34,700 --> 00:14:37,420
♪I thought you were an angel♪

175
00:14:37,500 --> 00:14:39,720
♪An angel who watched over me♪

176
00:14:39,740 --> 00:14:42,780
♪And saw every side of me♪

177
00:14:42,860 --> 00:14:45,420
♪Until reality is flooded♪

178
00:14:45,500 --> 00:14:47,660
♪You become sensible♪

179
00:14:47,740 --> 00:14:52,220
♪You are finally
out of touch with reality♪

180
00:14:52,530 --> 00:14:55,060
♪I hear the mountains, the seas,
and the people♪

181
00:14:55,140 --> 00:14:57,100
♪All clamoring because of you♪

182
00:14:57,220 --> 00:14:59,180
♪Hiding in the cape after the rain♪

183
00:14:59,340 --> 00:15:01,620
♪I cannot hear you♪

184
00:15:01,660 --> 00:15:05,140
♪So I opened my arms one last time♪

185
00:15:05,300 --> 00:15:08,660
♪But you escaped through the gap♪

186
00:15:08,770 --> 00:15:10,980
♪I saw winters come and summers go♪

187
00:15:11,020 --> 00:15:13,140
♪And thought there was ample time♪

188
00:15:13,380 --> 00:15:15,180
♪Cannot withstand the waves♪

189
00:15:15,300 --> 00:15:17,280
♪But you always make me panic♪

190
00:15:17,340 --> 00:15:21,580
♪How ridiculous, making me learn♪

191
00:15:21,660 --> 00:15:24,940
♪How much I am worth♪
